<div>
  <div class="text-center pt-2">
    <h1>Tens a certeza que queres<br> uma nova companhia?</h1>
    <p>Responde a este inquérito para avaliarmos se tem o que é<br> preciso para adotar um novo companheiro.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-5 d-flex gap-3">
    <div>
      <form action="/adopt/form" method="post" class="fs-5">
            <div>
              <div><label>É casado?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="married" id="married" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="married">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="married" id="married" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="married">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Tem filhos?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                  <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="childs" id="childs" value="option1">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="childs">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                  <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="childs" id="childs" value="option2">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="childs">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="live_with" class="form-label">Com quem é que vive?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="live_with" name="live_with" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Todas as pessoas em sua casa concordam com a adoção?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="home_agreement" id="home_agreement" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="home_agreement">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="home_agreement" id="home_agreement" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="home_agreement">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Alguém em sua casa tem alergias ou asma?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="allergies_in_relatives" id="allergies_in_relatives" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="allergies_in_relatives">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="allergies_in_relatives" id="allergies_in_relatives" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="allergies_in_relatives">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="main_caregiver_name" class="form-label">Quem é que vai ser o cuidador principal?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="main_caregiver_name" name="main_caregiver_name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Está preparado/a para cuidar deste animal por 10-15 anos?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="caregiver_long" id="caregiver_long" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="caregiver_long">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="caregiver_long" id="caregiver_long" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="caregiver_long">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="caregiver_illness_name" class="form-label">Quem é que vai cuidar do animal se ficar doente ou incapaz de o fazer?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="caregiver_illness_name" name="caregiver_illness_name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="why_adopt" class="form-label">Porque é que quer adotar um animal?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="why_adopt" name="why_adopt" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="address" class="form-label">Onde vive?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="address" name="address" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Tem quintal?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="yard" id="yard" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="yard">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="yard" id="yard" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="yard">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="animal_sleep_place" class="form-label">Onde é que o animal vai dormir?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="animal_sleep_place" name="animal_sleep_place" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Vai deixar o animal sozinho ao longo do dia?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="animal_loneless_daytime" id="animal_loneless_daytime" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="animal_loneless_daytime">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="animal_loneless_daytime" id="animal_loneless_daytime" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="animal_loneless_daytime">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="animal_alone_place" class="form-label">Onde é que o animal vai ser deixado sozinho?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="animal_alone_place" name="animal_alone_place" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Vai ter tempo para brincar com o seu animal?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="playtime" id="playtime" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="playtime">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="playtime" id="playtime" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="playtime">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Já teve algum animal de estimação antes?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="pet_before" id="pet_before" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="pet_before">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="pet_before" id="pet_before" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="pet_before">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Tem atualmente algum animal de estimação?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="pet_nowdays" id="pet_nowdays" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="pet_nowdays">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="pet_nowdays" id="pet_nowdays" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="pet_nowdays">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <div><label>Tem possibilidades de pagar todas as despesas veterinárias?</label></div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="animal_cares_expenses" id="animal_cares_expenses" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="animal_cares_expenses">Sim</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="animal_cares_expenses" id="animal_cares_expenses" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="animal_cares_expenses">Não</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="teach_plans" class="form-label">Como planeia ensinar o seu animal?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="teach_plans" name="teach_plans" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="moving_home_animal_effects" class="form-label">O que fará ao animal se mudar de casa?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="moving_home_animal_effects" name="moving_home_animal_effects" required>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <label for="give_up_circumstances" class="form-label">Em que circunstâncias desistiria do seu animal?</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="give_up_circumstances" name="give_up_circumstances" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-check pt-4">
              <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="defaultCheck1" required>
              <label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1">
                Autorizo a utilização dos dados inseridos, em conformidade com a Política de Privacidade
              </label>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center pt-4">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
            </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="card" style="width: 16rem;">
          <img src="/images/logo/dog.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="logoDog">
          <div class="card-body text-end">
            <h4>Nome</h4>
            <h5>Data de nascimento</h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
</div>

<style>
  .form-bar{
    width: 50rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background-color: rgba(29, 29, 27, 0.11);
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .rdo-style{
    background-color: rgba(29, 29, 27, 0.11);
  }

</style>